{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8da16780e9","title":"关于中央系统整风工作领导问题的批语R","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"647a45c7f5","index":0,"year":1950,"month":9,"day":1,"articleId":"8da16780e9"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"45a8063ccb","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"8da16780e9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"安子文，当时任中共中央组织部副部长。"},{"id":"b21f35049f","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"8da16780e9","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央华北局1950年8月29日关于华北局秘书处支部整党整干经验给分局、各省市委并报中央的电报。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c3d6105d1e","type":"title","text":"关于中央系统整风工作领导问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"8da16780e9"},{"id":"45a8063ccb","type":"paragraph","text":"安子文同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"8da16780e9"},{"id":"b21f35049f","type":"paragraph","text":"中央系统整风工作现在不知已开始进行否？是什么机关领导的？我认为应由中央组织部领导，由安子文同志负主责，由中央、军委、政务院、工青妇各系统各指定几个人组成委员会，领导整风工作。华北局此件时可印发各机关作参考材料。如何进行，盼告。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"8da16780e9"},{"id":"046f901b3e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"8da16780e9"},{"id":"c502879171","type":"paragraph","text":"九月一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"8da16780e9"}],"page":{"id":"bbcde65036","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"8da16780e9","start":126,"end":126}}}},"__N_SSG":true}